Hi Lukas, it sounds like you might be experiencing a sync issue between the ad management and billing sections. To resolve this, please try the following steps:
1. Ensure that you are logged into the correct account.
2. Refresh the page or log out and log back in.
3. Clear your browser cache and cookies.
4. If the issue persists, please contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
You can also refer to our Billing Guide for more information: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide).
